1Q.
Write a simple String program to take input from user?


import java.util.*;
public class q15_1 {
    public static void main(String [] args)
    {
        Scanner obj = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s;
        System.out.println("Enter your name here");
        s=obj.nextLine();

    }
    
}


2Q.
How do you concatenate two string in java?Give an example?
Ans.
The Java String concat() method concatenates one string to the end of another string.
class Concatenate {
  
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        String s = "Hello ";
        
        s = s.concat("World");
 
        System.out.println(s);
    }
}

3Q.
how do you find the length of a string in java explain with an example?
Ans.
public class length {
    public static void main(String []args)
    {
        String s="shahzad";
        System.out.println("Length of the string - "+s.length());
    }
    
}


4Q.
How do you compare two Strings in java? give an example?
Ans.
public class compare_string {
    public static void main(String []args)
    {
        String s1="Shahzad";
        String s2="shahzad";
        System.out.println("Comparision of two string "+s1.equals(s2));
    }

}


